</text><head history_name="廊坊爱德堡医院" text_name="" /><body id="C58F99B1"><emrtextdoc version="1.0" checkcount="0" senior=""><underwritemarks /><docsetting title="" id="" modifytime="20171130142739" version="1.0" lineSpacing="8" paragraphSpacing="8" defaultFontSize="12" defaultEnglishFontName="Times New Roman" defaultFontName="宋体" /><pagesetting paperwidth="827" paperheight="1169" leftmargin="98" topmargin="177" rightmargin="59" bottommargin="79" paperkind="A4" /><script runpwd="" editpwd=""><![CDATA[]]></script><head history_name="廊坊爱德堡医院" text_name="剖宫产知情同意书" section_id="8578994" bed_name="15" bed_id="8588076" section_name="妇产科" gender="1" sick_area="妇产科护理单元" /><body id="C1EC5944723"><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">诊断：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">手术指征：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">一、拟定采取的手术方式：子宫下段剖宫产术。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">二、拟施手术方案可能发生的母儿并发症：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">1</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.可能出现麻醉意外，详见麻醉同意书。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">2</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.术中、术后发出血，可能发生休克，有可能需输血，切除子宫。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">3</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.羊水栓塞、</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">DIC</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">、心脏骤停等，导致孕产妇死亡。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">4</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.术中血肿形成，损伤膀胱、肠管、输尿管，需扩大手术范围或再次手术。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">5</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.腹部切口血肿、感染、脂肪液化、延期愈合、裂开。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">6</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.术后可能发生下肢静脉血栓形成、肺栓塞、肠粘连、子宫内膜异位等。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">7</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.剖宫产儿因未经过产道挤压，易发生胎儿窘迫、新生儿窒息及肺炎，新生儿面神经损伤，新生儿缺血缺氧性脑病。新生儿窒息复苏后遗留脑损害而出现智力损害、肢体功能障碍，新生儿窒息复苏不成成致新生儿死亡。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">8</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.胎儿入盆深及胎头浮动者，术中可能需要产钳助产，此时兼有产钳助产的并发症。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">9</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.新生儿畸形不除外。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">10</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.术后避孕，再孕需间隔</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">2</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">年。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">11</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.除上述情况外，上可能发生其他并发症，或者需要提请患者及家属特别注意的其他事项，如：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    </span><span fontname="Times New Roman" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">12</span><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">.有可能发生罕见、目前尚未发生过、尚无医学报道的意外情况。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">三、术中更改诊疗方案授权：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    本人明白医疗尚有局限和不可预知性，因此□同意，□不同意在我的手术过程中，或我意识不清的情况下，需要更改手术或诊疗方案时，授权我的委托人代替我与医师共同商定。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">四、术中紧急情况处置授权： </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">    本人明白除了医生告知的危险以外，还有医疗操作或手术均有可能出现的其他危险，并且在手术中可能会发生预想不到的情况。在此，我授权医师在遇到预料之外的情况时，从考虑本人利益角度出发，按照医学常规予以处置，尤其是发生紧急、危险情况时，本人□同意□不同意授权医师可以即时处置。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">五、知情、免责同意签字：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">     我和我的家属已经认真阅读了上述内容，医生已用通俗易懂的话给和我的家属做了解释，并且让我们对不了解的内容进行了提问。我们已经了解手术和麻醉可能发生以上并发症，我们已经接受医学并不是一门非常精密的科学，尚不能在术前做出准确判断或预测的观点，理解医生在术前尚无法做出任何承诺。在理解医学的局限性和有可能出现的并发症和意外后。我和我的家属要求在爱德堡医院行剖宫产术。对有可能出现的并发症和意外均表示知情和理解：上述情况一旦发生，本人对此有充分的思想准备，并积极配合医生治疗，按规定缴纳一切费用。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">患者签字：                                      家属签字：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">                                                  </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">                                                与患者的关系：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">  </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">洽谈手术医师签字：                              决定手术医师签字：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">签字日期：                                       记录日期：</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000"> </span><p operatercreater="0" /></body></emrtextdoc></body></emrtextdoc>